Package: rbiorxiv
Type: Package
Title: R client for the bioRxiv API
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Nicholas", "Fraser", email = "nicholasmfraser@gmail.com",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: rbiorxiv is an R client for interacting with the bioRxiv API
    (https://api.biorxiv.org/). Functions include retrieving metadata of
    preprints, details of published papers associated with preprints, and
    summary and usage statistics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/nicholasmfraser/rbiorxiv
BugReports: https://github.com/nicholasmfraser/rbiorxiv/issues
Imports:
    httr (>= 1.3.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.5.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
